description: Ireland's chief medical officer urges people "not to go ahead" with bookings to travel abroad.
title: Coronavirus: 'Worrying trend' of rising cases in Ireland
title_page: Coronavirus: 'Worrying trend' of rising cases in Ireland - BBC News
maintext: He urged people who have made bookings to travel abroad for holidays "not to go ahead with that booking" rather than risk picking up Covid-19 or bringing it back to their community.
